content:
You are here:

Service Cloud
Einstein Conversation Mining Report Results

Review your Conversation Mining reports and act on the top contact reasons by adding them to a bot.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Einstein Conversation Mining is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience with the Service Intelligence add-on. Setup for Einstein Conversation Mining is available in Lightning Experience.
Available in: Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Viewing Einstein Conversation Mining Reports
When you click a report name, the main page shows contact reasons. You can filter contact reasons by conversations with agents or bots.

Acting on Einstein Conversation Mining Reports
You can send contact reasons to a bot or intent from the Einstein Conversation Mining page.
Create a Dialog from an Einstein Conversation Mining Report
Create a bot dialog based on a contact reason directly from Einstein Conversation Mining.
Add to a Dialog from an Einstein Conversation Mining Report
Send excerpts from a specific contact reason to an Einstein Bot dialog.
Create an Intent from an Einstein Conversation Mining Report
You can add excerpts to an intent thatâ€™s part of an intent set directly from Einstein Conversation Mining. Then, share the intents across many bots.
Add Excerpts to an Intent from an Einstein Conversation Mining Report
If you have an intent set and want to add excerpts to an intent, you can move them directly from Einstein Conversation Mining.

title: Maximizing Service Efficiency with Einstein Conversation Mining
